********************** TPC_DS Q31
EXPLAIN select /*TPC-DS Q31*/ i_item_id
,i_item_desc
,i_current_price
from item, inventory, date_dim, catalog_sales
where i_current_price between 26 and 26 + 30 and inv_item_sk = i_item_sk
and d_date_sk=inv_date_sk
and d_date between cast('2001-06-09' as date) and (cast('2001-08-08' as date))
and i_manufact_id in (744,884,722,693)
and inv_quantity_on_hand between 100 and 500 and cs_item_sk = i_item_sk
group by i_item_id,i_item_desc,i_current_price
order by i_item_id
limit 100;
Query Plan
=================================================================================
|ID|OPERATOR                                |NAME         |EST.ROWS|EST.TIME(us)|
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|0 |EXCHANGE IN REMOTE                      |             |3       |905         |
|1 |└─EXCHANGE OUT REMOTE                   |             |3       |900         |
|2 |  └─LIMIT                               |             |3       |890         |
|3 |    └─MERGE DISTINCT                    |             |3       |890         |
|4 |      └─SORT                            |             |4       |890         |
|5 |        └─NESTED-LOOP JOIN              |             |4       |889         |
|6 |          ├─HASH JOIN                   |             |3       |841         |
|7 |          │ ├─TABLE FULL SCAN           |date_dim     |1       |22          |
|8 |          │ └─HASH JOIN                 |             |3       |819         |
|9 |          │   ├─TABLE FULL SCAN         |item         |3       |14          |
|10|          │   └─TABLE FULL SCAN         |inventory    |3053    |548         |
|11|          └─DISTRIBUTED TABLE RANGE SCAN|catalog_sales|2       |16          |
=================================================================================
Outputs & filters:
-------------------------------------
  0 - output([item.i_item_id], [item.i_item_desc], [item.i_current_price]), filter(nil)
  1 - output([item.i_item_id], [item.i_item_desc], [item.i_current_price]), filter(nil)
  2 - output([item.i_item_id], [item.i_item_desc], [item.i_current_price]), filter(nil), rowset=256
      limit(100), offset(nil)
  3 - output([item.i_item_id], [item.i_item_desc], [item.i_current_price]), filter(nil), rowset=256
      distinct([item.i_item_id], [item.i_item_desc], [item.i_current_price])
